========================================================================
Reserved slot: coinbase/x402 SDK
========================================================================

The reference facilitator here (`src/facilitator/X402Facilitator.sol`) is a
minimal implementation authored for CI use. It does not vendor the
`coinbase/x402` reference SDK. When the SDK is vendored in a future
milestone (M2 candidate), the vendored source path, commit, and upstream
license grant will be recorded in this section. Until then, the reference
facilitator's shape follows the public `coinbase/x402` protocol description
without copying source.

========================================================================
