========================================================================

  - x402 protocol shape: Coinbase / x402 Foundation (coinbase/x402).
  - EIP-3009 `TransferWithAuthorization` shape: EIP-3009 specification.
  - `SpendPermissionManager` shape: Coinbase spend-permissions manager on Base
    (session-key delegation-cap primitive).
  - Circle USDC on Base mainnet:
    `0x833589fCD6eDb6E08f4c7C32D4f71b54bdA02913` (canonical target for
    live-mainnet runs; not vendored here).

Each of the above informs the shape of the reference facilitator and
